title: Cozy 2 Bedroom Available August!  $1,240
posting_body: ['A 2 bedroom unit is available at Sage Park Apartments.', 'Sage Park offers the residents a wide verity of amenities for residents convenience and relaxation.', 'Be prepared to enjoy our 2 Indoor Pools, 2 Saunas, A Fitness Room, A Billiard Room.', 'Sage Park has A rentable community room for family events and A Guest Suite for your visiting guest.', 'Laundry Rooms are available for you convenience and rentable Garage parking is also available.', 'Be prepared to make sage park your new home, Conveniently located and close to Walmart, Rosedale shopping center and Hwy 694 & 35', 'Pet Policy:', 'Cats and Dogs allowed.', 'There is breed restriction for dogs and there is pet fees as well.', 'Contact leasing office for more information.', 'Rental Requirements:', 'Income (2.5 times the rent amount) , Credit, Rental History, Criminal Background all are reviewed during application process.', 'Call leasing office for more information.', 'To Schedule a tour call Sage Park leasing office at the number below.', 'Office Information:', 'Address: 900 W County Rd D New Brighton, MN 55112', 'Number:', 'show contact info', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday - Thursday 9:00am - 6:00pm', 'Friday 8:00am - 5:00pm', 'Saturday - Sunday we are Closed', 'Website: <URL>', 'Professionally managed by Goldmark property management', 'Prices are subject to change , based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply.', 'Sage Park does not participate in any Voucher programs.']
